      • setFontHeight

        void setFontHeight(short height)
        set the font height in unit's of 1/20th of a point. Maybe you might want to use the setFontHeightInPoints which matches to the familiar 10, 12, 14 etc..(将字体高度设置为1/20点的单位。也许您可能想使用与熟悉的10、12、14等相匹配的setFontHeightInPoints。)
        Parameters:
        height - height in 1/20ths of a point(高度-高度的1/20分)
        See Also:
        setFontHeightInPoints(short)

      • setFontHeightInPoints

        void setFontHeightInPoints(short height)
        set the font height(设置字体高度)
        Parameters:
        height - height in the familiar unit of measure - points(高度-熟悉的测量单位中的高度-点)
        See Also:
        setFontHeight(short)

      • getFontHeight

        short getFontHeight()
        Get the font height in unit's of 1/20th of a point.

        For many users, the related getFontHeightInPoints() will be more helpful, as that returns font heights in the more familiar points units, eg 10, 12, 14.

        (获取字体高度，单位为1/20磅。对于许多用户来说，相关的getFontHeightInPoints（）会更有帮助，因为它以更熟悉的点单位返回字体高度，例如10、12、14。)
        Returns:
        short - height in 1/20ths of a point(短-高度为1/20分)
        See Also:
        getFontHeightInPoints()

      • getFontHeightInPoints

        short getFontHeightInPoints()
        Get the font height in points.

        This will return the same font height that is shown in Excel, such as 10 or 14 or 28.

        (获取字体高度（单位为点）。这将返回与Excel中显示的相同的字体高度，例如10、14或28。)
        Returns:
        short - height in the familiar unit of measure - points(矮--熟悉的测量单位-点中的高度)
        See Also:
        getFontHeight()

        int getIndex()
        get the index within the XSSFWorkbook (sequence within the collection of Font objects)(获取XSSFWorkbook中的索引（Font对象集合中的序列）)

        unique index number of the underlying record this Font represents (probably you don't care unless you're comparing which one is which)(此Font代表的基础记录的唯一索引号（您可能不在乎，除非您比较哪个是哪个）)
